====Usage notes====
Gender-neutrally written either {{ja-l|貴方}} or あなた. This kanji spelling is less common. An alternative spelling when referring to a female is 貴女 and for a male 貴男. See also {{ja-l|方}} (かた), {{ja-l|男}}, {{ja-l|女}}.

